<paragraph id="9C7FA31503020900FF43B4C6C8ACCCF4" blockId="38.[142,1427,1171,1220]" pageId="38" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis id="AEB47F0703020900FF43B4C6CAE3CC97" bold="true" box="[142,674,1171,1191]" pageId="38" pageNumber="65">
Figure 24. 
